00:02:35.439 --> 00:02:39.780
and shining out on to the drawing which means
his head's closer to us which means there

00:02:39.780 --> 00:02:44.560
should be a shadow cast from it. So we're
going to continue with the shading effects

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:52.799
